ng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Tr%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%8Bch-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-5cWUhusg0C6bW2KbrMcBvg">Trừ tịch kỳ 3 - 除夕其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/T%E1%BB%AB-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-minh-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-CmcW-aGSq0U6WnbHUzXRPg">Từ Ân tự bi minh tịnh tự - 慈恩寺碑銘并序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BA%A1c-Nam-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%91i-chu-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u/poem-qn_-zow5u279ayUfI0wP0g">Vọng nhạc (Nam nhạc phối chu điểu) - 望岳（南嶽配朱鳥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
